scene.message:
Yukino: This Tartarus — is it{nl}
also Yuriko's treasure vault?{nl}
There sure are a lot of{nl}
chests.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey...{nl}
once we beat "the Snow{nl}
Queen"...{waitkey}{clearbox}once we save Ms. Saeko,{nl}
it all ends, right? Everyone{nl}
goes back to normal{waitkey}and we get to go home, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I worry about Ms.{nl}
Saeko, but... is that Inaba{nl}
all right? He's a fool, that{nl}
one...{waitkey}Damn it, how frustrating!{waitkey}{ret}
